  "properties": {
    "title": "NATS iFACTS Planning Data",	
    "description": "A bespoke service delivered to NATS to support their Interim Future Area Control Tools Support (iFACTS) system. iFACTS is a NATS system that is designed to reduce ATC workload and to increase the overall capacity of the UK ATC system. This service gives NATS access to data at T+72 for planning purposes.  It provides wind and temperature forecast data for 5 locations and 3 levels. It is produced daily.",	
